name: Deadly Sweet Canvas
description:
This scrumptious canvas is the next in the series of my sweet skull and crossbone designs! 

The canvas is deep edged and measures 10x10 inches, painted using acrylic paint and has an extra bit of glitter to add to the gorgeousness of it!

name: Sweet Tooth canvas
description:
This delicious cupcake design has a darker side with the skull and cross bones incorporated into it, still looks yummy though!

A 10x10inch, deep edge canvas is painted with acrylic paint with a smother of glitter glue for that extra sparkle!

name: Comic Book Words
description:
We all love comic books, dont we? Well now you can love these! Famous and funny comic book words such as these POW! and KABOOM! will be the perfect present for any comic book lover, or even get one for yourself!  

All handmade and carefully cut out felt shapes range in sizes and colours, and of course words...but no bigger than 5 inches,  depending on the word of course! Others include ZAP! BANG! SNAP! WHAM! and many more! Please state which word and colour scheme you would like by putting a message in Paypal when purchasing.

name: Cupcakes
description:
These cute little treats come in a variety of colours (but sadly not flavours!) and all have googley eyes and funny facial expressions. Perfect for any cupcake lover, each one has a loop on their head so they can be hung off whatever you like! 

Each felt cupcake is roughly 3 inches tall, not including loop, and are available in yellow, blue, lime green, bright pink, purple, orange, and pale pink. A random one will be sent, or if there's a colour you prefer then please put a message in the PayPal box when purchasing.

name: Little Monsters - Randolph
description:
Randolph is the baby of the Little Monsters bunch, and walks around screaming all day when the others wont play with him!

He's completely hand made from bright pink and lime green felt with green stitching, and is 4.5 inches tall, quite big for a little fella! Please give him a home so he's got someone to play with!
